{
  "stem": "3449.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But be on your guard.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And then about three days later, he says, I think this is it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You better run.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Tell your immediate family, run.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I don't care where they run.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So my aunt told her parents.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But all the people-- where do you run?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see what I'm saying?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where do you hide?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There's no forests.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "See, if there were-- if there were forests immediately, you can run into the forest and hide.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "You had no place to run, because every Ukrainian had the right to kill you.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They-- they thought all the Jews had the money.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So naturally we're walking around with diamonds in your pocket.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So there was really no place to run, unless you made certain arrangements, or somehow like [? red ?] dug a hole in the floor or something like that.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Then you had a chance.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You had a chance-- the immediate hiding place.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "My father was starting to think seriously.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Once she told-- well he was thinking about that before.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My father also had a gun, which was completely-- I mean, he would-- if they ever find one, the whole family's gone.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But he figured, what have I got to lose?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Because at least if they come here, he says, I'll kill one German, at least for sure.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And that would give him the satisfaction.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "In the meantime, he was finding-- and he found a place near Lawrow.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "It's just outside of Lutsk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was like a little-- a halfway camp for German.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was on a main route.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when a German battalion came by, they had to be fed and all.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That would be the [? bundes ?] station where they would stop.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And it was like a little village.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
